No. 09-11061. William C. Pringle, Petitioner v. EMC Mortgage Corporation, et al. 562 U.S. 950, 131 S. Ct. 135,

178 L. Ed. 2d 248,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7713. October 4, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.

The Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
